description:
Approach

Descent

Trip report shows many rappels and drops in this canyon. We documented all of them and stayed in the watercourse for beta. Some of these drops can be down-climbed or bypassed on the hillside by skirting around them. So the number of rappels can be reduced for parties wanting to do the canyon that way.

Background

First descent by Michelle Nilles, 24 Dec 2016, solo. Rode Honda CT110 motorbike up South Park road, and came down from the top. Only did 3 rappels. Got out after dark. Hiked back up next day to recover the motorbike.

earlier trips in 2008 by Rick Kent & teams, and evidence of even earlier parties going there
